{'category': 'News', 'content': '<h1>关于评选四川大学成都地区法学校友会“独角兽”奖学金的通知 <span>发布时间：2016-11-23 21:35:55, 已阅读：484次</span></h1> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="line-height: 300%; color: black; font-size: 12pt">各位同学：</span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="line-height: 300%; background: white; color: black; font-size: 12pt">四川大学成都地区法学校友会为支持教育事业和公益事业，回馈母校，设立了“独角兽”奖助学金，旨在激励</span>\n <span style="line-height: 300%; background: white; font-size: 12pt">我院<span style="color: black">学生积极进取，促进学生努力学习和成长进步。现将具体通知如下：</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n &nbsp;\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><strong><span style="color: black">一、申请条件</span></strong></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">该奖学金的评选范围为法学院全日制在读的本科生、硕士研究生和博士研究生。</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">&nbsp;1、基本条件：</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（1）热爱祖国，遵守国家法律、法规及学校规章制度；</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（2）尊敬师长，关心集体，团结同学，有良好的品德修养；</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（3）学习勤奋，成绩优良，身心健康，且无挂科及重修；</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">2、选择条件（至少符合其中一个条件）：</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（1）积极参加校友会工作，表现突出；</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（2）担任学生干部，积极为同学服务，获得过校级表彰；</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（3）热心公益，在志愿服务方面成绩突出；</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（4）在法学专业类竞赛中，成绩突出；</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">（5）其他方面表现突出，如见义勇为等。</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><strong><span style="color: black">二、奖励名额及额度</span></strong></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">奖励名额：10人。金额：每人2000元人民币。</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">推荐名额：<strong>15</strong><strong>人</strong></span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><strong><span style="color: black">&nbsp;三、评审程序：</span></strong></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><strong><span style="color: black">&nbsp;1、学生申请</span></strong></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">申请奖学金的学生须由本人向辅导员提交书面申请，统一填写《四川大学法学院2015-2016学年“独角兽”奖学金申请表》（见附件），并附上学年成绩单（教务处下载，经学院教务员认定并加盖公章），各项荣誉证书复印件，以及其他相关证明材料。</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">成绩单及所取得的各项荣誉，证明材料均应在2015年9月1日至2016年8月31日期间获得，发表的论文须见刊，并附上复印件。由学院根据上述时间节点和要求务必对申请学生的各项荣誉、成果等做好审核工作。</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><b><span style="color: black">申请材料于11月28日下午4点前交到各年级辅导员处。</span></b></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><strong><span style="color: black">2、推荐和审定</span></strong></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">学院按照以上评选条件和学校奖学金的相关评选程序，组织班级民主评议，由学院奖助学金评审委员会择优选出该奖学金的推荐人选，在学院网站上公示3天，无异议，由学院汇总申请材料报校友会审核。</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n <span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: black">校友会将推荐名单和相关材料汇总，组织评审委员会，由评审委员会面试确定<strong>10</strong><strong>名</strong>初步获奖学生名单，法学院在网站上公示5天，无异议，确定最终获奖名单。</span></span>\n</div> \n<div style="line-height: 300%; text-indent: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char">\n &nbsp;\n</div> \n<div> \n <br> \n <table style="margin-left: 50px;" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="file"> \n  <tbody>\n   <tr> \n    <td colspan="2" class="header">相关附件</td> \n   </tr> \n   <tr> \n    <td width="75%">文件名称: <font style="font-size:14px;">独角兽奖学金申请表.doc</font> </td> \n    <td width="25%"> <a target="_blank" class="download" href="http://law.scu.edu.cn/download?portalId=725&amp;aid=75308&amp;filename=2016112321440684129.doc"> <font face="Wingdings" size="3">&lt;</font>下载 </a> </td> \n   </tr> \n  </tbody>\n </table> \n</div>', 'time': '2016-11-23T13:35:55Z', 'title': '关于评选四川大学成都地区法学校友会“独角兽”奖学金的通知', 'academy': '法学院', 'originURL': 'http://law.scu.edu.cn/detail.jsp?portalId=725&cid=8385&nextcid=8572&aid=75308'}